olour-first-listen-759185">A Flash Flood of Color</a> ”直接引用了以色列在歌曲“Stalemate”中使用磷弹的情况。去年 11 月，他们还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">Architects</a>等机构一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-the-last-dinner-party-architects-and-more-sign-open-letter-for-music-for-a-ceasefire-3536081">签署了一份停火公开信</a>。</p><p>他们加入了 IDLES 等乐队的行列，这些乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/idles-show-solidarity-with-palestine-at-tangk-launch-show-in-brixton-3588996">昨天刚刚在布里克斯顿举行的“Tangk”发布会上表达了对巴勒斯坦的声援</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-express-solidarity-with-palestine-at-wembley-arena-gig-3589108">《Enter Shikari》在温布利体育场演出中表达对巴勒斯坦的声援的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
